{"tid":1853842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東瀛遊下午尖沙咀派1800個口罩 港人將優先獲派 需出示香港身份證","createTime":"2020-01-31T07:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T08:13:38.000Z","uid":212626,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed1deb3ad6341709715e90b0b8380ed4493541c","tid":1853842,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"東瀛遊(06882)將於下午向市民免費派發1800個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n東瀛遊在facebook公布，因應疫情蔓延，公司管理層啟動危急應變小組，近日聯絡日韓嘅合作夥伴，至今搜集到2萬個口罩，第一批由日本導遊運送抵港，其餘口罩亦會在未來幾日陸續到達。<br />\n<br />\n該公司宣布，於今日下午4點半於尖沙咀其士大廈分行，率先向市民免費派發其中1800個，每人可以獲5個口罩，名額360個，會以派籌形式進行。港人將會優先獲派，並需要出示香港身份證。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2365442/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2365442%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=7410360e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2365442/</a>"},{"pid":"a812bb167eecbe1220e0f902dd182f07759bd04b","tid":1853842,"uid":29080,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:48:10.000Z","msg":"港人優先<br />\n私人公司得<br />\n政府唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b25439fe35dbb5505067d8321c494ddc327d27","tid":1853842,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23e543ac7f9fc6835173e0b4feb236dbe2f3cfa","tid":1853842,"uid":255637,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個成日出黎講野既高層 藍到仆街 都肯派口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f7c1a560bddfe9bf71936c8fdde3697e7b1893","tid":1853842,"uid":79993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sco